etymology.value: Likely a variant of Svetlana, a name of Slavic origin meaning 'light'.

usage_notes.explanation: Swetiana is a relatively uncommon given name. It is likely a variant of the more common name Svetlana.

readability_explanation.text: Swetiana is a proper noun, specifically a given name. Its readability would depend on familiarity with names of Slavic origin.
